definitions.definition: A unit of mass used in India , equal to the mass of a silver rupee coin, fixed at 180 troy grains ( 11.663 8038 grams ) in 1833, and of a similar but slightly variable value before that date.

main_definition: A unit of mass used in India , equal to the mass of a silver rupee coin, fixed at 180 troy grains ( 11.663 8038 grams ) in 1833, and of a similar but slightly variable value before that date.

definitions.definition: A South American grassland shrub of the genus Parastrephia .

main_definition: A South American grassland shrub of the genus Parastrephia .
